anybody." ; Photo, COLOR, At left, Gillespie explains how she'll implement 
Proposition 103 at a news conference May 11, one week after the state Supreme 
Court upheld most of the law's provisions. Above, conferring with press 
secretary Carey Fletcher. Dan Escobar; Photo, COLOR, Proposition 103 has made 
its author, Harvey Rosenfield, famous. He's got the copies of Esquire and 
