<P>
JUNK MAIL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
How much do junk mail and flyer ads contribute to the 1.5 tons of trash that 
each local resident sends to the dump every year? If Assemblywoman Marian La 
Follette (letter, May 24) could find a cure for the paper pestilence of 
unsolicited advertisements, she'd reduce the trash from my household by 50%. 
</P>
<P>
MARGARET W. ROMANI 
