houses along the coast near Papeete.; Photo, COLOR, Woman, above, wades in the 
ocean searching for fish. ; Photo, COLOR, Schooner, top left, sails peacefully 
into the sunset in the calm waters off the island of Tahiti.; Photo, COLOR, 
while a local entertainer, right, performs at a hotel on Moorea. ; Photo, 
