The Odyssey of an American Warrior 
</P>
<P>
by Col. David H. Hackworth (U.S. Army, ret.) and Julie Sherman 
</P>
<P>
(Simon &amp; Schuster: $24.95; 875 pp.) 
</P>
<P>
"Hackworth's memoir is the story of a boldly adventurous life spent in the 
