<DATELINE>
<P>
PORT VILA, Vanuatu 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Five people have died and 350 have fallen ill in an epidemic of dengue fever in 
the popular South Pacific tourist resort of Vanuatu, health officials said 
Friday. 
</P>
</TEXT>
