SUSPECTED BOMB FOUND 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Reuters 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
CAIRO 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A package believed to contain a bomb was found Saturday on the grounds of the 
American Cultural Center in Cairo. A U.S. Embassy spokeswoman said a "probable 
explosive device" was discovered hidden under a shrub at about 12:45 p.m. and 
removed. She gave no further details. 
</P>
