<HEADLINE>
<P>
DINING IN NICE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
I read Beverly Beyer and Ed Rabey's article on Nice ("Footloose," May 21) with 
interest because I was there in March and happened to eat at La Belle Nicoise. 
It was good, but I enjoyed the fish and selection more at Grand Pavois-Chez 
Michel, 11 Rue Mayerbeer, near the Promenade des Anglais. Elegant atmosphere, 
and the owners really made me feel welcome. Highest recommendation. 
</P>
<P>
LORI SANDERS 
</P>
<P>
Los Angeles 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
