children, who did not accompany them to getaway weekend for mothers at Big Bear 
Lake. ; Photo, Carol Smith-Carter mixes lore and laughs during boat ride. ; 
Photo, Campers roast marshmallows on the beach over portable bonfire after 
Saturday supper. TONYA EVATT / Los Angeles Times; Photo, COLOR, 
Founder-director Carol Smith-Carter on trail ride at Mother's Camp. 
</P>
