<TEXT>
<P>
Italy's Flavio Giupponi outsprinted Laurent Fignon of France to win the 14th 
stage of the Tour of Italy bicycling race at Corvara, but Fignon took over the 
pink jersey as the overall leader from Erik Breukink of the Netherlands. 
</P>
