<HEADLINE>
<P>
ENJOYS HIS READING 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
This letter is simply to let you and your staff know that I truly enjoy reading 
the Real Estate section. As a homeowner, I find the tips on house maintenance 
and repair to be quite useful, and I especially look forward to the Q &amp; A 
section on buying and selling real estate. This section always has a wealth of 
information for anyone who wishes to purchase or sell his own home. 
</P>
<P>
My wife and I own only our house, and we appreciate that the majority of your 
section is devoted to average homeowners like us rather than to wealthy real 
estate developers (as are most real estate sections). Perhaps in the future you 
could provide information on selecting general contractors for remodeling 
projects. Maybe even a "Consumer's Report"-style ratings approach. 
</P>
<P>
JOEL FIERBERG 
</P>
<P>
Montebello 
</P>
