<P>
ACCIDENTS -- ORANGE COUNTY 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA060489-0230 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 66382 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
June 4, 1989, Sunday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
