left along back row: William A. Honigman, Craig Scott, Allan Songstad, Norman 
F. Garton, Leon A. Bosch, Philip S. Borden, James Dukette, Melody Carruth and 
Herbert Schwartz on extreme right. In foreground are Patricia Ann Gummeson, 
Janice Graham, in white jacket, Bernard Kuai and Bea Hassel Rogatz, with 
shoulder bag. Not pictured is Karl Gustav Schneider II. DON TORMEY / Los 
Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
